Start PIXIJS
npm init -y

using npm install
//used sudo command if you are not in the main root path /

sudo npm install pixi.js --save

for development:

sudo npm install browser-sync

lodash.map v4.6.0

The lodash method _.map exported as a Node.js module.
Installation

Using npm:

$ {sudo -H} npm i -g npm
$ npm i --save lodash.map

//Replace "start" content to:
"browser-sync start --server --files '*.js'"



